== 主要災情 ==
[[女川核電廠|女川核電廠]]有三分之二的緊急冷卻系統故障，含有放射性的水溢出，裸露出3個[[用過核燃料|用過核燃料]]池，但廠外輻射數據並無太大變動<ref name=USAtoday>{{cite web|url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/ondeadline/post/2011/04/74-magnitude-earthquake-hits-japan-tsunami-alert-issued/1|title=New quake disrupts power to cooling unit at nuclear plant|date=7 April 2011|author=Stanglin, Douglas|publisher=USA Today|work=content.usatoday.com|accessdate=2011-04-09|archive-date=2012-07-09|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120709085239/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/ondeadline/post/2011/04/74-magnitude-earthquake-hits-japan-tsunami-alert-issued/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[福島第一核電廠|福島第一核電廠]]雖無更大的損害傳出，但以安全為考量的情況下暫時撤出員工。

有4人死於這場地震，包括[[山形縣|山形縣]]一名因醫療呼吸系統斷電而身亡的老婦人<ref name=deaths />。另外至少有141人被割傷、瘀傷或骨折<ref name=USAtoday />。少數的民宅與道路出現損害情形<ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/asiapcf/04/07/japan.quake/?hpt=T1|title=Fresh aftershock in Japan rouses fear, kills 2|work=edition.cnn.com|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|author=CNN Wire Staff|date=8 April 2011|accessdate=2011-04-17|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117112556/http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/asiapcf/04/07/japan.quake/?hpt=T1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

